                    "question": "已知 $A_1, A_2, A_3$ 为一完备事件组, 且 $P\\left(A_1\\right)=0.1, P\\left(A_2\\right)=0.5, P\\left(B \\mid A_1\\right)=0.2, P\\left(B \\mid A_2\\right)=0.6, P\\left(B \\mid A_3\\right)=0.1$,则 $P\\left(A_1 \\mid B\\right)=()$.",
